  <section id="venue"> 
   <h1>Conference venue</h1> 
   <p>The conference will be held Lockheed Martin's Antarctic Support Contract (ASC) meeting facility located at: </p>
   <address> 7400 S. Tucson Way<br> Centennial, CO 80112 </address> 
   <iframe width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?q=7400%20S%20Tucson%20Way%2C%20Centennial%2C%20CO%2C%20United%20States&amp;key=AIzaSyCKRMeOJaxyWwi3EBU_Hwr13SozwSfeL3o"></iframe> 
   <p></p> 
  </section> 
  <section id="hotel"> 
   <h1>Conference hotel</h1> 
   <img class="img-thumbnail pull-right" style="margin-left: 1em" src="http://www.hawthorn.com/common/images/branded/BH/images/46504_b1.jpg"> 
   <p>Arrangements have been made with the <b>Hawthorn Suites</b> for a reduced group rate for PTC attendees. The Hawthorn Suites is located in the Denver Tech Center and is 2.5 miles from the conference venue. A block of rooms will be set aside for PTC attendees and need to be reserved by <b>March 9, 2015</b>. PTC attendees are responsible for making and paying for their own accommodations as required. They are free to make their arrangements anywhere of their choosing. Reservations can be make online at <a href="http://www.hawthorn.com/hotels/hotel-overview?propId=BH46504&amp;rate_code=LXPF">Hawthorn Suites by Wyndham</a>. Click on the <em>Special Rates &amp; Codes</em> button and enter the Rate Code <b>LXPF</b> to receive the conference rate of $89/day. </p> 
   <address> <b>Hawthorn Suites by Wyndham</b> <br> 6780 South Galena Street <br> Centennial, CO 80112 <br> 1-800-996-3426<br> 1-303-792-5393<br> </address> 
  </section> 
